  "detailed_description": "Army of One is a first person shooter game. Battle against other players in various modes from 1 on 1 to 32 on 32 and show that you or your team are the best one-man armies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn army of one, from the casual player to the most professional player, they managed to have fun and find ways and challenges at their level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a ranked mode by rank and skill level you can face people of your own level to have fun and prove that you are the best.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArmy of One also features both individual and team weekly tournaments in demolition mode, where you need to blow up the enemy base.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn army of one you can improve and customize your equipment, from your knife to your operator, with 9 operators available, each with a unique skill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCome now to Army of one the new Free to play shooter and show your skill.",
  "about_the_game": "Army of One is a first person shooter game. Battle against other players in various modes from 1 on 1 to 32 on 32 and show that you or your team are the best one-man armies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn army of one, from the casual player to the most professional player, they managed to have fun and find ways and challenges at their level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a ranked mode by rank and skill level you can face people of your own level to have fun and prove that you are the best.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArmy of One also features both individual and team weekly tournaments in demolition mode, where you need to blow up the enemy base.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn army of one you can improve and customize your equipment, from your knife to your operator, with 9 operators available, each with a unique skill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCome now to Army of one the new Free to play shooter and show your skill.",
